column37: The Visable system had some nice polished features that I either didn't notice or couldn't find in the prototype. The ability to compare rate changes and differences between datacases was a nice feature.

column37: I don't like black background ! Again, some drag and drop features would be cool. Oh and maybe more insights when clicking to a bar of the barchart, or a point in the scatter plot ( not just giving the possibility to include or exclude the selected item)

column36: I feel like the filter out thing took some time to discover. I had no idea what that did. It was a little confusing to use. Plus there was no proper way to remove it. I just had to click on a blank space on the screen.
column37: I like that I have the ability to use the kind of graphs I want. It allows me greater flexibilty. Only thing was the difference in variables over the three graphs. Sometimes it was confusing but I think you may just have to spend more time with it.
